1. *Biste* li mi pomogli? (Would you help me?)
2. Ja bih *bistao* tu da vidim šta se dešava. (I would be here to see what's going on.)
3. *Biste* li se ikada vratili kući? (Would you ever come back home?)
4. Ona bi *bila* najsrećnija na svetu. (She would be the happiest in the world.)
5. *Biste* li mi učinili uslugu? (Would you do me a favor?)
6. Ja bih *bio* iznenađen time. (I would be surprised by that.)
7. *Bisti* siguran da ćeš uspeti. (Be sure that you will succeed.)